title: Savior.avi
description: After losing his beautiful wife and young son in a terrorist bombing, Joshua Rose avenges their death in a murderous rampage. To escape his crime, he joins the Foreign Legion and assumes the name of Guy. But as a mercenary for the Serbs, Guy is still possessed by his mission of vengeance - until he meets Vera, a young Serb girl pregnant with her Muslim rapist&#039;s child. Together they embark on an unforgettable journey of survival through a war-shredded world. He is her only hope for survival. She is his only chance for redemption.
